data.description: Completely remodeled and updated ranch villa with open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, wide doorways and ZERO entry (no stairs)!  This seller completely updated the entire villa last year including:  new flooring, new paint throughout, updated kitchen including quartz countertops, backsplash, plus new sinks and faucets throughout home.  Electric fireplace was updated last year with new unit and brick surround.   New water heater, additional blown-in insulation and new garage door opener added and wood fence for the private patio was installed.  HOA takes care of lawn care, snow removal, roof repair/replacement, clubhouse and property entrance.   This maintenance-free villa is located in Santerra - conveniently located off North Oak with easy access to shops and restaurants.
